data.description: Cash sale only.  Handyman special.  Spectacular opportunity for the taking!  Custom, split level home offering three bedrooms and two full baths.  Wonderful floor plan with lots of space for entertaining.  Many upgrades have been started and just need the finishing touches.  This home is nestled in a quiet neighborhood and offers the convenience of easy access to I45 and to many nearby restaurants, shopping, service amenities and more!  Awesome backyard deck invites you to enjoy the great outdoors beneath the shade of mature trees.  Home being sold as is.  No repairs will be made. Visit today to see your family's next home.
